Params: {1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory96.png'}
{2: '...Are we there yet?', 3: '4'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'We should be near, I think...', 4: '1'}
{2: '???', 3: 'Looks like I was right scouting ahead of time.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "You must not have been aware, but you've gone off course by two kilometers. You'll end up in the Arctic Ocean if you go any farther.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: 'But the virtual compass indicates...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "...Oh, you. All your magnetic navigation systems have to be recalibrated in the Arctic. The Earth's magnetic fields overlap here, so compasses tend to deviate.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "I'll lead the way. Otherwise, all the frozen venison we got is going to become shoe leather from the bonfire.", 4: '1'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory96.png'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'How does it feel being back?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'The last time we met was after the battle of Kowloong, huh.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Yeah... Though I only have the backup data from my memories of that time.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'You had no choice after all. You had to protect 【kuroname】.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "It's great just being able to talk to you again like this.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: 'Us Forest Guards think highly of your actions.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: 'After all, sacrifice and redemption are two key aspects of our creed. We sincerely respect all brave and noble people.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'Well, we think the same for the Forest Guards as well.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'I heard from Murray that Babylonia always wanted to officially thank the Forest Guards for their help in the battle of Kowloong, but Rosetta declined.', 4: '1'}
{3: "Diana's expression stiffens, but she remains silent."}
{3: 'She walks in silence, her horns shaking with each step. The rest of you can only follow in silence as well.'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Diana', 3: "...It's Rosetta after all.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "It's nothing. As long as we are of help.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Diana', 3: "We won't let this affect our alliance with Babylonia.", 4: '1'}
